subtitle: Överflöd Entity MT
content:
GTA+ Members can claim the Överflöd Entity MT super car for free through June 5.

Treat speed limits like suggestions in the Överflöd Entity MT (Super). Members can claim one for free from The Vinewood Car Club this month, and outfit it with performance upgrades and cosmetic customizations at Hao’s Special Works.

GTA+ Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
